channel.title: Cant connect
channel.description:
Hi there, I have a server which was all working and everyone could connect and stuff...
But the next day, nobody could connect.. I put in my ip from No-ip but it didnt work, I put left the ip blank and I could connect, so it has something to do either with my no-ip or my router, and yes, I have forwarded the ports for TCP and UDP..[br][br][size=1]Posted on: November 16, 2008, 12:23:00 pm[/size][hr]Help please.. There is other people helping others when their topic is about one small thing.. Please..
